  <fr:mainmatter>
    <html:p>Give a <fr:link href="/008C/" title="Time-dependent vector field" uri="https://kellenkanarios.com/008C/" display-uri="008C" type="local">vector field</fr:link> <fr:tex display="inline"><![CDATA[v_t]]></fr:tex> one can construct a time-dependent diffeomorphic map called a <html:em>flow</html:em> <fr:tex display="inline"><![CDATA[\phi : [0,1] \times  \mathbb {R}^d \to  \mathbb {R}^d]]></fr:tex> defined via the ordinary differential equation
<fr:tex display="block"><![CDATA[\begin {align*}
  \frac {\mathrm {d}}{\mathrm {d}t} \phi _t(x) &= v_t(\phi _t(x)) \\
  \phi _{0}(x) &= x
.\end {align*}]]></fr:tex></html:p>
  </fr:mainmatter>
